};

  name: "过滤条件",
  type: "container",
  data: {
    title: "过滤条件",

    height: 30,
    left: 0,
    top: 0,
    titleAlign: "left",
    titleColor: "rgba(188, 201, 212, 1)",
    hideTitle: false,
    labelColor: "",
    background: ""
  }
};

export { BASE_CONF, SIMPLE_CONF, BASE_CONF_DATA, FORM_CONTAINER_CONF };
